We eat here whenever we are  in town

Awesome as always, and HUGE portions that made almost two meals! The delivery person was also extremely sweet, considering the late hour. Always happy to order from you.

I paid for a cranberry juice  4.95 and it was a little coffee cup that you get from the deli, that was ridiculous but over all it was good the food
The breakfast sandwich was delicious as was the teas I ordered however the blueberry muffin I ordered toasted with butter was stale

Food comes back soggy.... I asked no tomato because I’m allergic and they of course put tomato so my girlfriend ended up eating it. They always mess up. Honestly the only reason I order there is because they are late hours. If you are looking for good quality? Look elsewhere. I gave 3
Stars instead of 2 because they were very fast. They also have promised multiple refunds to me in the past for messing up my order and never sent the refund. Lastly, 1 out of every 4 times I order here (which is often since I do work late a lot) my order is wrong.
They satisfied my hungrier that you Ritz Diner

Everything would have been excellent had I recieved everything I paid for. Great food, but due to non contact it's hard to make sure that you get all of the food you paid for. I will give them another try because the food really is good!

Everything was excellent!

Loved the customer service, the restaurant itself looked clean and fresh, and the food tasted good. Would visit again.
it was fine
